text: People got to understand that this is not a shop that you go in with tons of questions. It's a shop that contractors come to get their raw materials and equipments. Know what you want, ask clear and concise questions, and you'll usually find electrical equipments that you're looking for; don't go in asking every single layman questions. Indeed may not have consistent service all the time, but staffs have helped me well in many occasions. My go to place for electrical equipments and has many branches islandwide.
